### Question 108
Examine this code:
```javascript
function ( pOptions) {
  pOptions.firstDay = 1;
}
```
You add this code to the JavaScript Initialization Code attribute of a Calendar Region and reload the calendar.

What does this change do?

### Question 131
Examine this code:
```javascript
function( pOptions) {
  pOptions.minTime = "07:00:00";
  pOptions.maxTime = "18:00:00";
  return pOptions;
}
```
What is the result of applying the code in the Initialization JavaScript Code attribute for your Calendar component where the Show Time attribute is enabled and the Day View is selected by an end user?
